                            Pure value-add. No hard sell.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* FAQ Section */}
            <Section className="bg-[#f8fafc]">
                <div className="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    <Heading2 className="text-center mb-16">Frequently Asked Questions</Heading2>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <FAQItem
                            question="How is this different from a placement agent?"
                            answer="Placement agents are expensive (1-3% of capital) and use a pre-existing network. We help you build *your own* asset and pipeline at a flat fee, giving you control and long-term scalability."
                        />
                        <FAQItem
                            question="What kind of ROI can I expect?"
                            answer="If a new investor brings just $25k in lifetime fees and calls cost $500, closing at a measly 10% yields a 5x ROI. We'll map your specific potential ROI during our strategy session."
                        />
                        <FAQItem
                            question="How long until I see results?"
                            answer="Our system is built for speed. After a 14 day build-out, you can expect qualified investor calls on your calendar within 30 days of launch."
                        />
                        <FAQItem
                            question="Do you work with my asset class?"
                            answer="We work with multifamily, self-storage, industrial, VC, and more. The principles of targeting accredited investors are universal across these asset classes."
                        />
                        <FAQItem
                            question="Is this really SEC compliant?"
                            answer="Yes, 100%. Our process was developed with securities attorneys specializing in Rule 506(c). We ensure all advertising is fully compliant."
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Final Urgency/Scarcity Block */}
            <Section className="bg-[#0f172a] text-white text-center py-20">
                <div className="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    <Heading3 className="text-white mb-6">A Note on Our Capacity</Heading3>
                    <p className="text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                        We only partner with a limited number of new funds each month to ensure high performance. This is an operational reality, not a marketing tactic. If you are serious about building a pipeline this quarter, secure your spot today.
                    </p>
                    <ButtonPrimary className="w-full md:w-auto mx-auto bg-white text-[#11523c] hover:bg-slate-100 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200" onClick={scrollToCTA}>
                        Secure Your Spot
                    </ButtonPrimary>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Footer */}
            <footer className="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 py-16 px-6 md:px-24">
                <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8">
                    <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
                        {/* Secondary Icon Logo */}
                        <img
                            src="logo.png"
                            alt="Sequoia Icon"
                            className="h-10 w-10 object-contain"
                            onError={(e) => {
                                e.target.onerror = null;
                                e.target.style.display = 'none';
                            }}
                        />
                        {/* Fallback visual if logo fails to load (ensures layout stability) */}
                        <div className="flex flex-col">
                            <span className="font-serif font-bold text-xl text-[#112e4a] leading-none">Sequoia</span>
                            <span className="font-sans text-xs tracking-widest text-[#11523c] uppercase mt-1">Strategies</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 md:gap-12">
                        <a href="#" className="text-slate-500 hover:text-[#11523c] text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
                        <a href="#" className="text-slate-500 hover:text-[#11523c] text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
                        <p className="text-slate-400 text-sm">
                            &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Sequoia Strategies. All rights reserved.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </div>
    );
}